Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.05,0:00:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年有水灾啊\N就是啊 收成肯定的不行了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.23,0:00:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本不知道会怎么样哦\N你只要想一件事就行了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.40,0:00:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊\N去宣穿一下 找女人过来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.25,0:00:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有女人到这个村子里来的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.09,0:01:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只知道吃饭\N很多男人还没有媳妇啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.94,0:01:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊 大概5个人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.44,0:01:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.29,0:01:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你？\N当然了 老婆死了有8年了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.63,0:01:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以再娶了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.47,0:01:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了在田里干活还有其他的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.81,0:01:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相白了吗\N你儿子不是有老婆了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.65,0:01:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白我守护这个土地的心情的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.82,0:02:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么可能会守在温儿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.83,0:02:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,35岁了 老婆也跑了\N和不知道哪个个地方女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.83,0:02:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结婚后 她会待在这儿吗\N绝对会跑了的旺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.34,0:02:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还没有和那个女人见面吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.51,0:02:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吧\N但是你没有女人没关系吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.02,0:02:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说什么啊 快去带女人来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.36,0:02:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.04,0:02:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.38,0:02:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和他是2年前结婚的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.22,0:03:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和他都是2婚哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.05,0:03:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说他和他前妻性格不合哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.06,0:03:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很老实温柔\N也许这个不合吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.90,0:03:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有细问他 我和他相反哦\N非常外向哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.91,0:03:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经厌倦了和前夫的生活\N所以分手了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.42,0:03:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能这个的关系 和他脾气\N很合的来 非常融洽哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.60,0:03:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在东京的百货公司工作\N可能不适合吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.94,0:04:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发觉了以后\N就辞职了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.94,0:04:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不会白养活他的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.95,0:04:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有天他说在东京生活好痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.29,0:04:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定回到东北方\N老爸的老家生活了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.14,0:04:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我吧 我来拖吧\N马上就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.64,0:04:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空气真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.31,0:04:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以悠闲一下了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.65,0:04:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好累啊 休息一下吧\N说什么呢 马上到了加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.36,0:05:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,农家女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.39,0:05:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.40,0:06:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.41,0:06:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好累啊\N她是谁呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.58,0:06:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,介绍一下哦\N她是我老婆哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.75,0:06:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的来了啊 打个电话嘛\N我会去接的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.43,0:06:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很远吧 真的来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.93,0:06:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫乳房？\N是织田 赖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.10,0:06:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能是乳房呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.77,0:06:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事嘛\N不是说没有女人会过来的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.28,0:06:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的哦 刚才的话我收回哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.45,0:07:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个不是马 是牛的乳房哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.63,0:07:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家休息一下吧 累了吧\N回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.63,0:07:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这活怎么办啊\N拜托你了哦 回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.31,0:07:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没有想到会到乡下来哦\N欢迎哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.65,0:07:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁呀 牛的乳房哦 好大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.00,0:07:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸和我想象中的不一样哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.50,0:07:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬我想起来我的老公哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.51,0:08:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太突然了吧\N没有想到哦 村里面只有阿姨哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.69,0:08:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有就是大叔了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.86,0:08:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真大啊 太大了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.53,0:08:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢哦\N他说要回家我也跟过来了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.54,0:08:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎哦\N真的欢迎哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.88,0:08:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起生活吧\N这个家空空的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.88,0:08:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想把他租出去哦\N但是还是放弃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.72,0:08:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他是怎么认识的啊\N在一个公司认识的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.57,0:08:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是被搭讪认识的吗\N不可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.74,0:09:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像他那样不可能吧\N泡妞不行的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.91,0:09:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像啊 和以前见过的一样哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.92,0:09:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么集中精神还是听不进去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.76,0:09:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的事以前也发生过哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.61,0:09:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累了吧\N没有啦 没事哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.78,0:09:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天开始我就干活吧\N明天？不用勉强啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.13,0:09:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的啦 还要麻烦老爸的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.80,0:10:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不一样吧\N我和老爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.97,0:10:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸很好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.48,0:10:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候怀疑是不是有血缘关保哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.65,0:10:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我妈妈很像哦\N很好啊 挺高兴的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.99,0:10:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用勉强哦\N估计会处不好关系哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.50,0:10:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.69,0:10:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.19,0:11:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.70,0:11:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.04,0:11:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公很老实\N做爱也很少主动哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.88,0:11:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候会感到寂寞哦\N但是觉得这是小事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.15,0:13:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是死去的老婆穿的哦 当然了\N可以穿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.16,0:13:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始就是我的家人了\N那我去换衣服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.16,0:13:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这儿换吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.00,0:13:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,农家的女人没关系的啦\N就在这儿换
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.17,0:13:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去田里干活都是一样的啦\N也是哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.01,0:13:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是骗你哦\N都是这样的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.35,0:13:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快换吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.36,0:13:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦\N就在那儿换 吧快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.34,0:16:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.35,0:16:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了啦\N走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.69,0:16:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得很好哦\N好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.54,0:16:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这儿哦\N好喜欢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.71,0:16:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的吧\N继续干活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.05,0:17:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腰要注意哦\N要不然会疼的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.39,0:17:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿要用方哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.40,0:17:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快继续吧，要带有爱意哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.74,0:17:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样才行哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.08,0:17:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续哦 腰挺直了这儿用力哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.42,0:17:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快继续干活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.26,0:17:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 放在一起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.76,0:17:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,压在一起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.77,0:17:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了用力压哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.27,0:17:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 这儿要用力哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.94,0:17:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦\N老爸你也干活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.28,0:18:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起来干活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.96,0:18:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样割哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.30,0:18:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了吗\N试试吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.30,0:18:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点哦 这样拿好了割哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.31,0:18:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腰要用力哦\N大腿张开哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.15,0:18:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟尿尿一样哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.49,0:18:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的哦\N再张开一点哦 对了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.33,0:18:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大咪咪太大了会碍事哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.17,0:18:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸挺起来哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.34,0:19:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快挺起来哦\N对了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.86,0:19:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么和他结婚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.87,0:19:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他很温柔哦\N只是这个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.04,0:19:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这个？\N他不行啊 不能给女人饭吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.38,0:19:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的啦 我会加油的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.39,0:19:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油？一个人加油也不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.90,0:20:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啦\N哪个?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.57,0:20:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边啦\N哪边？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.58,0:20:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啦\N老爸快住手啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.58,0:20:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在等这个吧\N不要了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.92,0:20:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想要吗\N真的快住手啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.93,0:20:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很寂寞吧\N什么寂寞啊 快住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.44,0:20:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.78,0:20:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要的吧\N不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.78,0:20:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 快住手啊\N很爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.46,0:21:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想要吧\N快住手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.96,0:21:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.80,0:21:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手啊\N我不会对他说的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.48,0:21:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那身体满足不了你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.99,0:21:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的才是你想要的哦 这么硬哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.66,0:21:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是女人哦 想要男人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.17,0:21:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.34,0:21:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着你的身体就能硬的男人\N喜欢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.52,0:22:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.70,0:22:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.87,0:22:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.71,0:22:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会让你爽死的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.38,0:22:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要啦\N让我舔乳头哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.06,0:22:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腰都在动了哦\N没有啦 这儿不能碰的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.57,0:22:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿不行的啦\N让我来帮你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.07,0:22:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要吧\N真的不行的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.24,0:23:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的啦\N好热啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.91,0:23:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的啦\N不行？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.09,0:23:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿不行?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.92,0:23:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很爽吧
