Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:41.70,1:06:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要舔干净才行哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:46.87,1:06:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊 住手啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:52.88,1:06:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看仔细哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:57.38,1:06:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:02.89,1:07:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:11.23,1:07:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要阿\N为什么不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:15.90,1:07:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干净了啦 好了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:20.07,1:07:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快放了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:24.57,1:07:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股也脏了啦\N那儿没有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:32.08,1:07:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的啦\N看都脏了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:40.26,1:07:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股翘起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:43.09,1:07:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要了啦\N翘高点哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:53.77,1:07:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:08.12,1:08:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊\N这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:14.46,1:08:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翘高点啊，舔了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:26.47,1:08:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:30.97,1:08:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:41.15,1:08:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:44.49,1:08:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不舔不行哦\N不要了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:06.18,1:09:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有干净哦\N不要了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:27.70,1:09:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴里面要舔干净哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:39.21,1:09:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:01.73,1:10:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样啊\N让我看清楚哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:09.91,1:10:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会帮你舔干净的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:17.91,1:10:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:25.76,1:10:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有味道哦\N哪里啊 这儿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:31.59,1:10:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这儿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:38.60,1:10:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有里面啊\N不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:53.28,1:10:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一步了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:58.12,1:11:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:03.46,1:11:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:09.13,1:11:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:39.33,1:11:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:03.19,1:12:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才对不起哦 和你公公没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:14.03,1:12:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在担心儿子不行\N老婆会不会又跑了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:27.38,1:12:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有老婆已经6年了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:36.22,1:12:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里的年轻人都组团相亲哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:43.23,1:12:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不行的\N那这儿的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:51.40,1:12:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一半还是处男哦\N是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:00.24,1:13:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了哦\N等一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:09.42,1:13:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要感谢一下你的手纸哦\N不行的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:20.93,1:13:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要误解哦 平常不是这样的啦\N只是现在哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:26.94,1:13:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能做爱哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:31.94,1:13:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直没做过吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:37.61,1:13:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:43.62,1:13:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:50.46,1:13:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:55.30,1:14:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不行的啦\N不吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:03.31,1:14:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的啦 他会知道的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:12.82,1:14:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:24.33,1:14:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都这么硬了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:29.00,1:14:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有段时间没做啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:26.22,1:15:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有年轻女人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:32.40,1:15:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:39.90,1:15:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:49.91,1:16:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大啊\N真的像是牛的乳房哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:10.60,1:16:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:19.94,1:16:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好软啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:43.13,1:16:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:48.47,1:16:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没这样了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:13.16,1:17:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:29.35,1:17:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊\N第一次被这样夹哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:39.02,1:17:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:18.39,1:18:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:38.91,1:18:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:44.75,1:18:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会这么享受哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:25.46,1:19:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:01.16,1:20:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太脏了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:28.19,1:20:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:34.70,1:20:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:44.87,1:20:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:49.71,1:20:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:21.91,1:21:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要了啦\N脏的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:36.43,1:21:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了这个村子以后我变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:40.76,1:21:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这自然环境中\N已经忘了不是道德的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:11.46,1:22:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小美啊\N好久不见啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:18.97,1:22:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:27.31,1:22:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分手了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:29.81,1:22:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是前妻打过来的电话哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:35.65,1:22:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公是个老实人哦\N这样不行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:42.99,1:22:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实已经感觉到那是懦弱哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:49.83,1:22:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是讨厌我才走的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:55.34,1:22:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也不讨厌哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:19.03,1:23:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:25.87,1:23:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也来喝一杯吧\N好的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:36.38,1:23:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢哦\N快喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:44.22,1:23:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 我回东京了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:50.89,1:23:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和他分手了\N等一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:59.74,1:24:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的原因吗 那我道歉哦\N不是的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:06.58,1:24:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸说得很对哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:18.25,1:24:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你们添麻烦了 对不起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:31.10,1:24:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛\N真的对不起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:40.61,1:24:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个村子留不住女人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:46.78,1:24:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N不用说了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:10.14,1:25:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要哭了啦\N真的对不起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:25.15,1:25:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然已经想好了\N最后能
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:40.34,1:25:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 又坚强又温柔\N喜欢你色眯眯哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:45.57,1:26:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起哦\N爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:16.60,1:27:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊 继续哦\N喜欢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:58.64,1:27:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:21.66,1:28:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗\N对了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:31.34,1:28:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:44.02,1:28:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:00.37,1:29:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢强壮的男人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:08.54,1:29:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢色眯眯的男人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:16.72,1:29:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢这样吧\N你选对了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:26.06,1:29:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:55.26,1:29:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:26.62,1:30:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快摸啊 对了哦\N这儿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:35.30,1:30:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那儿哦\N喜欢硬邦邦的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:10.67,1:31:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要吗\N好想要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:40.03,1:31:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快让我摸摸哦
